{"tid":1552503,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"油麻地阿叔怒屌藍絲廢老（有片）","createTime":"2019-09-08T10:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T11:49:12.000Z","uid":245301,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"58ea1a4b4caf596e87dd5a355ca4724d3d3167f9","tid":1552503,"uid":245301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:45:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wd-Fab06AxI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fwd-Fab06AxI&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMK2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=91ce9643\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wd-Fab06AxI</a><br />\n<br />\n岩岩油麻地有個死藍絲廢老係咁歌頌大陸，見到個紋身阿叔本身以為佢都係藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點知原來係深黃，屌撚到個阿叔無聲出，最後叫佢死番大陸共享大灣區榮華<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個藍絲仲話popo打得太溫柔，之後成班阿叔話到時出解放軍打柒佢老母就知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：有出聲屌個藍絲，係咁屌佢老母屌到佢無聲出"},{"pid":"14488c2a5bf825881645e8a647aa8fec6f6fafb6","tid":1552503,"uid":167721,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:49:07.000Z","msg":"宜家已經唔可以憑外觀分藍黃<br />\n除非著住件愛國衫<br />\n利申：返馬會，有部分賭馬賭波阿叔好黃"},{"pid":"73b389cf2c564a0d5c95dec3ead1bf9b14d786f6","tid":1552503,"uid":245301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:50:03.000Z","msg":"感動到想喊見到班阿叔真心為港發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60850210ae2c20ada74ac24c811f929b5175f5c8","tid":1552503,"uid":245301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:54:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0f09aca637b2c0c38e5b8add1f84e34d7700350","tid":1552503,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14488c2a5bf825881645e8a647aa8fec6f6fafb6","tid":1552503,"uid":167721,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:49:07.000Z","msg":"宜家已經唔可以憑外觀分藍黃<br />\n除非著住件愛國衫<br />\n利申：返馬會，有部分賭馬賭波阿叔好黃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:02:23.000Z","msg":"呢句真"},{"pid":"604